{"prompt": "Generate a website for a edtech platform. The website should be innovative and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EduSpark</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f48fb1; /* Light Pink */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --card-background: #fce4ec; /* Very Light Pink */\n            --button-hover-color: #c62828; /* Darker Red */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 60px auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card {\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-card h3 {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-card p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--brand-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            background-color: var(--card-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple Responsive Adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.8em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .features {\n                grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n            }\n            .cta h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.1em;\n            }\n            .cta h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                padding: 12px 25px;\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons - you would typically link this in the head -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Ignite Your Learning Journey</h1>\n        <p>Discover cutting-edge courses, interactive tools, and personalized learning paths designed to empower your future.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                <h3>Innovative Content</h3>\n                <p>Engaging video lectures, hands-on projects, and real-world case studies.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                <h3>Expert Instructors</h3>\n                <p>Learn from industry leaders and passionate educators.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                <h3>Personalized Paths</h3>\n                <p>AI-driven recommendations to guide you towards your goals.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <h2>Ready to Spark Your Potential?</h2>\n        <p>Join thousands of learners transforming their careers and lives.</p>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Today</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EduSpark. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // JavaScript can be added here for more complex interactions\n        // For example, smooth scrolling for anchor links, animations, etc.\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}